1. File & Directory Permissions
Task:
Create /devops_workspace
 ->mkdir devops_workspace

Create a file project_notes.txt.
 ->touch project_notes.txt

Set permissions: Owner can edit, group can read, others have no access.
 ->chmod 640 project_notes.txt

Use ls -l to verify permissions.
total 0
-rw-r----- 1 vboxuser vboxuser 0 Jan 27 13:17 project_notes.txt
